## 5. UI/UX Architecture

### A. Navbar
- **Style:** Glassmorphism (`bg-white/80`, `backdrop-blur-md`)
- **Positioning:** `sticky top-0 z-50`
- **Responsive Heights:** 72px (mobile) → 80px (lg) → 88px (xl)
- **Links:** Productos, Talleres, Aprende, Nosotros, Mayoreo
- **CTA:** Solid black "Ordena" button with Instagram icon

### B. Homepage Hero
- **Layout:** Full-width video background with right-aligned floating card
- **Video:** Autoplay, muted, loop with parallax scroll effect
- **Card:** White background, premium shadow, responsive sizing
- **Accents:** Kanji overlays (静岡, 抹茶), coordinates

### C. Product List Page (PLP)
- **Filter Bar:** Todo | Matcha | Té en Polvo | Té Hoja Suelta | Kits | Accesorios
- **Grid:** 3-column (desktop), 2-column (tablet), 1-column (mobile)
- **Cards Include:**
    - Square image with hover zoom
    - Category labels (small caps)
    - Product name + Kanji
    - Starting price
    - Adaptive technical specs table
    - "Ver Producto" CTA

### D. Product Detail Page (PDP)
- **Static Generation:** All pages pre-rendered at build time via `generateStaticParams`
- **Dynamic Metadata:** SEO title, description, OpenGraph per product
- **Layout:** 60/40 split (gallery / sticky info)
- **Features:**
    - Image gallery with thumbnails
    - Size selector (30g, 100g, etc.)
    - Price display (MXN)
    - "Añadir al Carrito" CTA
    - Technical specs table (adaptive by type)
    - Flavor Profile grid (tea only): Dulzor, Umami, Amargor, Cuerpo
    - Brewing Guide (tea only): Temperatura, Ratio, Tiempo

## 6. Technical Stack
- **Framework:** Next.js 15 (App Router)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS
- **Language:** TypeScript
- **Fonts:** Inter (sans), Cormorant (serif), Space Mono (mono), Noto Serif JP (kanji)
- **Architecture:** 
    - Server Components for SEO & static generation
    - Client Components for interactivity (filters, galleries, size selectors)

## 7. Responsive Typography
Base font size scales for larger displays:

| Breakpoint | Font Size | Increase |
|------------|-----------|----------|
| < 1024px | 16px | — |
| ≥ 1024px | 17px | +6% |
| ≥ 1440px | 18px | +12.5% |

## 8. Data Architecture
Centralized in `src/data/products.ts`:

```typescript
// Types
type ProductSpecs = TeaSpecs | AccessorySpecs | KitSpecs;
type FilterCategory = "all" | "matcha" | "polvo" | "hoja" | "accesorios" | "kits";

interface Product {
  slug: string;
  name: string;
  kanji: string;
  subtitle: string;
  labels: string[];
  image: string;
  images: string[];
  category: FilterCategory;
  sizes: ProductSize[];
  specs: ProductSpecs;
  flavorProfile?: FlavorProfile;
  brewingGuide?: BrewingGuide;
  description: string;
}

// Exports
export const products: Product[];
export const filters: { id: FilterCategory; label: string }[];
export function getProductBySlug(slug: string): Product | undefined;
export function getProductsByCategory(category: FilterCategory): Product[];
```

## 9. SEO Strategy
- **Static Generation:** All product pages pre-rendered for indexing
- **Dynamic Metadata:** Per-page title, description, OpenGraph, Twitter Cards
- **Semantic HTML:** Proper heading hierarchy, aria-labels, semantic sections
- **Local SEO:** Geo-targeting for Hermosillo, Sonora (coordinates in meta)

